Type: Package
Package: pluma
Title: Lightweight Code and Document Renderer
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Aline", "Moreau", , "aline.moreau@example.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 'pluma' is a lightweight rendering engine that converts code
    and text snippets into beautiful documents (HTML, PDF, DOCX).  It aims
    to be a minimal alternative to RMarkdown, offering modular output
    formatting, syntax highlighting, and flexible styling via templates.
    Designed for automation, scripting, and seamless integration in data
    pipelines.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/fictive-lab/pluma
BugReports: https://github.com/fictive-lab/pluma/issues
